00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:39,080
 ja sam tek bio mladim kapelan

956
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:41,520
 da ja dođem i malo o tome pričam.

957
00:31:41,520 --> 00:31:43,780
 Sad, ja sam već znao za teologiju tijela,

958
00:31:43,780 --> 00:31:45,840
 ali nisam znao detalje sve.

959
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:48,940
 Bio sam na jednom sutrtu u Skatsu

960
00:31:48,940 --> 00:31:52,200
 kao Luka ne, Luke neme,

961
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,120
 ajmo da uvod nasvi.

962
00:31:53,120 --> 00:31:54,200
 Jednom su mene zvali

963
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:54,880
 i ja se sjećam,

964
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,000
 pater volenik me zvao.

965
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:58,700
 I tada sam ja

966
00:31:58,700 --> 00:32:01,000
 sa rukavicama o tome pričao.

967
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:03,060
 Neko me otvoreno pitao o tome.

968
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,640
 Jedna studentica.

969
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:07,000
 Pazi, ovo je bilo dvije treće.

970
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:09,460
 Ona mene pita otvoreno javno.

971
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:11,660
 Šta vi mislite,

972
00:32:11,660 --> 00:32:12,360
 don da mi rekao,

973
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:14,560
 jedan par želi živit zajedno,

974
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:16,080
 želi...

975
00:32:16,080 --> 00:32:17,860
 Ja sam bio tako nejasan.

976
00:32:18,660 --> 00:32:21,140
 Ja nisam htio s jedne strane

977
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,440
 ići protiv crkve,

978
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:24,760
 ali nisam imao snage

979
00:32:24,760 --> 00:32:26,400
 to braniti javno.

980
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:28,700
 Jer nisi sam u sebi to...

981
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:29,560
 Jer nisam razumijel,

982
00:32:29,560 --> 00:32:30,780
 nisam to prožvako dovoljno.

983
00:32:30,780 --> 00:32:32,380
 Ja nisam imao hrabrost s nekom

984
00:32:32,380 --> 00:32:33,900
 reći, ne smijete živit zajedno,

985
00:32:33,900 --> 00:32:34,900
 nemojte to radit,

986
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:35,320
 to je zlo.

987
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:35,940
 A ona je rekao,

988
00:32:35,940 --> 00:32:37,060
 pa dobro, najmjerno mi želimo,

989
00:32:37,060 --> 00:32:39,560
 zar nije bolje prije nego poslije?

990
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:41,100
 Otkri da si ne pašemo prije nego poslije.

991
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:42,380
 Ja sam prešutio nauk.

992
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,840
 Sad nisam govorio protiv crkve,

993
00:32:44,300 --> 00:32:44,980
 ali sam prešutio.

994
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:46,780
 Nisi ga naglasio i objasnio.

995
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:49,660
 I tada jedna druga cura

996
00:32:49,660 --> 00:32:51,520
 se digla i rekla,

997
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:52,780
 sram vas bilo.

998
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:53,320
 Pred svima.

999
00:32:53,320 --> 00:32:53,680
 Tebi.

1000
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,060
 Meni.

1001
00:32:54,060 --> 00:32:55,920
 Sram vas bilo.

1002
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:56,420
 Pred svima.

1003
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:58,460
 Nemoj se...

1004
00:32:58,460 --> 00:33:00,720
 Pa to nisam nikad čula.

1005
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,820
 I ovo je ekskluziva.

1006
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:03,440
 Ovo je ekskluziva.

1007
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:05,180
 Ona je rekla,

1008
00:33:05,180 --> 00:33:06,720
 kako vi kao svećenika,

1009
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:07,840
 katolički svećenik,

1010
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:09,820
 ovdje pred svim mladima,

1011
00:33:09,820 --> 00:33:12,760
 ste prešutili nešto tako važno.

1012
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:13,500
 Ona vajda,

1013
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:14,820
 ja ne znam ko je to bilo.

1014
00:33:14,820 --> 00:33:16,420
 Ja bih volio sad njoj se zahvaliti.

1015
00:33:16,780 --> 00:33:17,960
 Što me prozvala.

1016
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,620
 Ako pogleda će, znači da.

1017
00:33:19,620 --> 00:33:20,700
 Dakle, prozvala me.

1018
00:33:20,700 --> 00:33:22,940
 Nešto sam govorio protiv šta.

1019
00:33:22,940 --> 00:33:24,040
 Ja sam prešutio.

1020
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:25,240
 Prešutio sam samo.

1021
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,920
 Ti si to, ono,

1022
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:28,620
 dao neki neutralni odgovor,

1023
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:29,180
 bez veze.

1024
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:29,880
 Sa rukavicama.

1025
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:31,560
 Samo da se ljudima svidim.

1026
00:33:31,560 --> 00:33:32,800
 Samo da se svidim ljudima.

1027
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:35,480
 Mene hladan znoj oblio.

1028
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:39,500
 Ona ti je rekla da kako možeš ti prešutiti

1029
00:33:39,500 --> 00:33:40,580
 na katoličke crkve.

1030
00:33:40,580 --> 00:33:42,120
 Zašto ne govorite jasno?

1031
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:42,920
 Istino, tako je.

1032
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:45,340
 Ja sam i to jedna studentica.

1033
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,020
 Ja sam išao doma.

1034
00:33:47,020 --> 00:33:48,320
 Ja sam pao u takvoj krizi.

1035
00:33:48,320 --> 00:33:51,060
 Pomogu misliti.

1036
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:53,360
 Ja sam nakon toga išao na studij i tako.

1037
00:33:53,360 --> 00:33:56,420
 I to je brojilo u mene.

1038
00:33:56,420 --> 00:33:57,720
 Ja sam se bacio u to.

1039
00:33:57,720 --> 00:34:00,700
 E, kad je Don Damir se vratio 2007.

1040
00:34:00,700 --> 00:34:02,560
 Više ne šuti.

1041
00:34:02,560 --> 00:34:05,000
 Ajmo sad do te teme.

1042
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:05,440
 Zašto?

1043
00:34:06,660 --> 00:34:07,800
 Ovo je moje iskustvo.

1044
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:13,920
 Nitko ne ide iz neke zle volje to činiti.

1045
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:15,820
 Ta pač je namjerna jako dobra.

1046
00:34:15,820 --> 00:34:16,700
 Ok?

1047
00:34:16,700 --> 00:34:17,680
 I da se razumijem.

1048
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:18,700
 Ja to imam u moj rodbini.

1049
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:20,200
 Ja to vidim.

1050
00:34:20,200 --> 00:34:21,420
 Mislim, svi to radim.

1051
00:34:21,420 --> 00:34:22,940
 Mnošto to čini.

1052
00:34:22,940 --> 00:34:24,300
 Dobro namjerno.

1053
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:24,660
 Ok?

1054
00:34:24,660 --> 00:34:25,620
 Uzmijemo da je dobro namjerno.

1055
00:34:25,620 --> 00:34:26,720
 Mislim, gdje je problem?

1056
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:33,100
 Problem je što djevojke ne razumiju kako mozak muški funkcionira.

1057
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:35,740
 Mi muškarci, mi smo kavaljeri.

1058
00:34:35,740 --> 00:34:36,940
 Mi smo lovci.

1059
00:34:36,940 --> 00:34:42,100
 Svaki muškarac voli se u dvara djevojci i tako dalje.

1060
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:42,700
 I on lovi.

1061
00:34:42,700 --> 00:34:46,480
 I ako on, ovo je na pocvestoj razini.

1062
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:47,800
 Ja sam dugo oveme razmišljio.

1063
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:50,520
 Ako on ulazi u neki brak.

1064
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:53,040
 I onda 5-6 mjeseci prije ide s njom živjeti.

1065
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:53,740
 I on je lovac.

1066
00:34:53,740 --> 00:34:55,980
 Kakav će on biti u ti 5 mjeseci?

1067
00:34:55,980 --> 00:34:56,700
 Naj, naj, naj.

1068
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:58,120
 Sve su prelative.

1069
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,320
 Zašto?

1070
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:01,020
 Jer zna da je na probi.

1071
00:35:01,020 --> 00:35:03,380
 I ova se oduševi.

1072
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:04,300
 Ajme, meni.

1073
00:35:04,300 --> 00:35:06,120
 On meni donose i doručak u krevet.

1074
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:08,420
 Pa on, on je tako uredan.

1075
00:35:08,420 --> 00:35:08,920
 On je.

1076
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:11,940
 I zašto?

1077
00:35:11,940 --> 00:35:12,540
 Jer on ju lovi.

1078
00:35:12,540 --> 00:35:14,060
 I on zna da ona to očekuje.

1079
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:17,140
 I onda nakon 6 mjeseci oni ulaze u brak.

1080
00:35:17,140 --> 00:35:17,720
 I on je ulovio.

1081
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:18,400
 Oženio se.

1082
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,160
 I šta se dogodi?

1083
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:20,920
 On se upusti.

1084
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:21,560
 Stvarnost.

1085
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:22,160
 Stvarnost.

1086
00:35:22,160 --> 00:35:22,860
 E sada.

1087
00:35:22,860 --> 00:35:24,740
 U čemu je problem?

1088
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:26,820
 Ona je stvarila

1089
00:35:26,820 --> 00:35:27,560
 jednu sliku

1090
00:35:27,560 --> 00:35:28,740
 koja je nije bila

1091
00:35:28,740 --> 00:35:29,520
 najrealnija

1092
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:31,380
 i gradila sve na tome.

1093
00:35:31,380 --> 00:35:32,840
 Ušla u brak

1094
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:35,420
 i videla da to ni baš nije tako.

1095
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:36,140
 On je se tamo

1096
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:37,760
 samo se tako predstavio.

1097
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:39,200
 On čak nije lagonamjerno.

1098
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:40,280
 Nego je muškarac bio.

1099
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:41,300
 Tipičan muškarac.

1100
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:41,820
 lovio je.

1101
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,620
 E sada.

1102
00:35:42,620 --> 00:35:43,240
 Koji je razlika

1103
00:35:43,240 --> 00:35:43,980
 ako nisu živjeli?

1104
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:45,740
 Ona ne bi imala tu pred sliku.

1105
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:47,660
 Odnosno tu uljepšanu sliku.

1106
00:35:47,660 --> 00:35:49,980
 Ona bi ušla

1107
00:35:49,980 --> 00:35:51,060
 bez ikakve slike.

1108
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:52,100
 Takve slike bar.

1109
00:35:52,100 --> 00:35:52,580
 Tako je.

1110
00:35:52,580 --> 00:35:54,180
 I ona bi ga prikvatila

1111
00:35:54,180 --> 00:35:55,380
 u zdravlju i bolesti

1112
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:56,240
 u dobru i u zlu.

1113
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:58,020
 Prije braka

1114
00:35:58,020 --> 00:35:59,240
 on se predstavljio

1115
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:00,740
 samo u dobru,

1116
00:36:00,740 --> 00:36:02,180
 u najboljem

1117
00:36:02,180 --> 00:36:04,740
 i onda ona opravdano pita

1118
00:36:04,740 --> 00:36:05,860
 pa dobro šta je sad ovo?

1119
00:36:05,860 --> 00:36:07,120
 Ok.

1120
00:36:07,120 --> 00:36:08,620
 Ja se ugrađujem

1121
00:36:08,620 --> 00:36:09,680
 oko moje teorije.

1122
00:36:09,680 --> 00:36:11,960
 Ja sam dugo o tome razmišljio

1123
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:13,300
 i to je zaključak

1124
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:14,240
 koji sam ja došao.

1125
00:36:14,240 --> 00:36:14,680
 Razumijem.

1126
00:36:14,680 --> 00:36:16,840
 Pojednostavio si jako

1127
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:17,960
 ali si nam sad rekao

1128
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,680
 kako ti to vidiš.

1129
00:36:18,680 --> 00:36:20,120
 Jer kako objasniti

1130
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:22,260
 da nakon kohapitacije

1131
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:23,240
 par godina

1132
00:36:23,240 --> 00:36:24,920
 da baš ti paravi

1133
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:25,720
 završe

1134
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:27,320
 nakon nekoliko mjeseci

1135
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,200
 što sam ja imao

1136
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:29,600
 u moje pastoralno iskustvo

1137
00:36:29,600 --> 00:36:30,220
 i kao župnik

1138
00:36:30,220 --> 00:36:31,060
 i kao studijski padan

1139
00:36:31,060 --> 00:36:32,700
 sam to vidio u mojim očima.

1140
00:36:32,700 --> 00:36:32,960
 Da.

1141
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:35,160
 I zato...

1142
00:36:35,160 --> 00:36:36,380
 Dakle, to je jedna razina.

1143
00:36:36,380 --> 00:36:36,560
 Je.

1144
00:36:36,560 --> 00:36:37,800
 Dakle, razina toga da

1145
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,520
 u stvari

1146
00:36:38,520 --> 00:36:41,260
 onima koji žele

1147
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:42,260
 da im to pomogne

1148
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:42,920
 da bolje

1149
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,320
 da se pripreme

1150
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,260
 u stvari za jedan

1151
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:47,140
 dugi, zajednički,

1152
00:36:47,140 --> 00:36:48,200
 lijepi život.

1153
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:48,440
 Ok.

1154
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,320
 A druga stvar je

1155
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,380
 nauk crkve.

1156
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:51,840
 Dakle, ovo je iskustvo

1157
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:54,000
 zašto to plodova?

1158
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:54,620
 A kako je?

1159
00:36:54,620 --> 00:36:55,720
 Zašto crkva toliko?

1160
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:57,860
 Zašto u nauku crkve stoji

1161
00:36:57,860 --> 00:37:00,100
 da ljudi ne žive zajedno

1162
00:37:00,100 --> 00:37:01,420
 viđu da se trebaju...

1163
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:02,620
 Ono što se kaže u medijima

1164
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:04,000
 seks samo u braku.

1165
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:04,200
 Je.

1166
00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:06,100
 Ja bi ovdje jednu razliku radio

1167
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:07,900
 jer stvarno postoji

1168
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:09,000
 jedna razina gdje

1169
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:10,920
 ako su neke situacije

1170
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:11,580
 gdje neko živi

1171
00:37:11,580 --> 00:37:12,520
 ispod istog krova,

1172
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:14,220
 a žive kao brat i sestra,

1173
00:37:14,220 --> 00:37:18,000
 ja to nikome ne preporučujem,

1174
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:20,980
 ali ako ćemo gledati usko,

1175
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:22,120
 to nije grijeh,

1176
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:22,900
 ono,

1177
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:24,380
 da su odvojni,

1178
00:37:24,380 --> 00:37:25,540
 evo,

1179
00:37:25,540 --> 00:37:26,520
 zbog nekih financijskih,

1180
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:27,500
 ekonomskih razloga

1181
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:28,140
 i tako dalje.

1182
00:37:28,140 --> 00:37:30,020
 Tako da,

1183
00:37:30,020 --> 00:37:31,880
 jako je važno gledateljima

1184
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:32,340
 to znat,

1185
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:34,300
 da oni mogu se pričestiti.

1186
00:37:34,300 --> 00:37:34,800
 Jako,

1187
00:37:34,800 --> 00:37:35,820
 jako na jednoj razini

1188
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:37,480
 čak možda rade javni sablas.

1189
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,200
 Ali nisam razumijela.

1190
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:38,400
 Dakle,

1191
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:38,760
 na primjer,

1192
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,400
 imaš, aha,

1193
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,860
 imaš dečka i curu

1194
00:37:40,860 --> 00:37:42,060
 koji žive u istom stanu,

1195
00:37:42,060 --> 00:37:43,260
 ne žive zajedno,

1196
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:44,560
 nemaju seksualne odnose.

1197
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:45,500
 Ko brat i sestra.

1198
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:46,180
 Ko brat i sestra,

1199
00:37:46,180 --> 00:37:47,080
 ali žive zajedno

1200
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:48,200
 zato jer je to praktičnije

1201
00:37:48,200 --> 00:37:48,940
 ili iz nekog druga razloga.

1202
00:37:48,940 --> 00:37:49,960
 Iz nekog nužda,

1203
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:50,200
 evo,

1204
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:51,420
 doselio je,

1205
00:37:51,420 --> 00:37:53,400
 stanarina bi bila skupa

1206
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:53,600
 i znači,

1207
00:37:53,600 --> 00:37:55,220
 mi moramo razumjeti ljude.

1208
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:56,020
 Da, da, razumijem.

1209
00:37:56,020 --> 00:37:57,540
 Ja sam pratio takve ljudi,

1210
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,500
 ljudi mene upozoruju

1211
00:37:58,500 --> 00:37:59,700
 kad dođu nekad na ispred na razgove,

1212
00:37:59,700 --> 00:38:00,680
 od časa samo da znate,

1213
00:38:00,680 --> 00:38:01,820
 živim ja s mojim momkom,

